title: Dark Angel's Love
features: A few months ago a doorway was discovered in a city buried thousands of years ago, the earliest sign of civilization on Earth that had ever been found. The walls had depicted people with wings; the archeologist leading the team had thought they represented angels mingling with man. That was until the door was activated and he stepped through discovering a world of beauty and full of people with wings. Enter Vanessa a spunky archeologist and the dark angel who falls in love with her...Can an angel and human make true love work?
description: I am not just a writer but an avid reader! I like to read a variety and I write because it makes me happy and allows me to use the voices in myhead for a good cause. To entertain other people the way other people'sstories entertain me.
